<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
	
	
<% if @cdata['group'] and @cdata['group'].logo.exists? then -%>
<img src="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/<%= @cdata['group'].logo.url %>"><br/><br/>
<% else -%>	
<img src="http://intermix.cr8.com/images/logo.gif"/><br/><br/>
<% end -%>

<div>
<%=raw @message %>
</div>

<hr/>


This is a message sent to a group you're a member of. <a href="<%= "http://unday.#{ROOTDOMAIN}/autologin?code=#{@cdata['recipient'].confirmation_token}" %>">Log in</a>
<% if false -%>
You can also see it in your <a href="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/messages">Message Area</a>
<% end -%>
<img src="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/pixel/<%= @cdata['message'].id.to_i if @cdata['message'] %>.gif" width="0" height="0" border="0" style="display:none">

</body>
</html>
